at.ac.tuwien.ict.andropicar.rmcs.stm32

Class RMCSControlComponent

  • java.lang.Object
    • at.ac.tuwien.ict.andropicar.rmcs.stm32.RMCSControlComponent
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    STM32SpiInterface

    public class RMCSControlComponent
extends java.lang.Object
    The RMCSControlComponent-class is a base-class for all components of the RMCS, that directly or indirectly control parts of the RMCS (e.g. drive, lights, etc.). Each object that is of the type RMCSControlComponent can process one or more types of IControlData.
    Each instance has its own UniqueLinkedBlockingQueue, which can be written to, to inform this component about new IControlData, which must be handled by sub-classes of RMCSControlComponent.
    Author:
    Boeck
